data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. **2022 ROOF** Welcome to Avalon Park! This community's theme is live, learn, work and play. In an excellent location, top rated schools, a plethora of amenities, and entertainment sit in your backyard. Avalon Park's renowned Downtown Avalon is home to restaurants, shops, eateries and professional services. The community regularly hosts events such as movie nights and festivals. You will love where you live. 4632 Atwood Place is a mirror of its community: luxury meets comfort. This almost 3000sqft home is nestled on .20 acres, backing up to pond and conservation. The lot is fenced in, creating so much privacy. Upon entry, your eye will immediately capture the gorgeous and calming water view. This home is truly a breath of fresh air with light from every corner, high tray ceilings, and oversized windows. Each guest in your home will have space and privacy, especially since this home has TWO master bedrooms. The non-primary bedrooms are generously sized and neatly tucked away to the left side of the home. The primary master suite retains two walk in closets and an oversized master bathroom. HOA dues include basic cable and Internet. Community amenities include bike trails, sports field, community pool, and a community center with a sauna, rental room and gym. You will never have to leave where you live.
